Package: polygons
Version: 0.1.9000
Title: Misc functions for calculating and drawing polygons
Description: Misc set of functions to compute and draw polygons. Among the functions
  included in this package are: piechart, a more versatile version of pie, colorRamp2,
  a faster implementation of colorRamp, npolygon, n-sided polygon, and, colorkey.
